             On the 13th of this Month. I was going from Ludgate-Hill up into Holbourn, I went thro' the New-Market, and a little before I came to the Corner of <placeName id="t17430629-24-crimeloc145">Holbourn-Bridge</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17430629-24-crimeloc145" type="placeName" value="Holbourn-Bridge"></interp>
